{"tid":2203416,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"未證被告自願招認 官拒口供呈堂","createTime":"2020-09-15T10:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T10:34:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bf0e9447e209db6090bf08305cff487954b103ce","tid":2203416,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:06:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/NXR6Q2ADDBF3RNVACE4WWMDGIQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FNXR6Q2ADDBF3RNVACE4WWMDGIQ%2F&d=ulKCtXgG4rwmRR8qyGKIuag2R%2FZNJK3LRZFq%2F1XEYLE%3D&h=7215b06b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200915%2FNXR6Q2ADDBF3RNVACE4WWMDGIQ%2F&h=73444879\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200915/NXR6Q2ADDBF3RNVACE4WWMDGIQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n未證被告自願招認 官拒口供呈堂<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/vjQbtYBXNIdcoZOsIDXKTXik-JA=/1207x679/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7Y7ERRMMSJHKHKHMBJQMBJIYVU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FvjQbtYBXNIdcoZOsIDXKTXik-JA%3D%2F1207x679%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7Y7ERRMMSJHKHKHMBJQMBJIYVU.jpg&h=c657c2a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■警員何釗華<br />\n<br />\n【藏雷射筆氣槍案】<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】。。。。。。。，直指曾有女警恐嚇他謂「堅持話冇就坐10年啦」，所謂招認實情是警員將自己調查所得綜合寫出，然後要求被告簽署。署理主任裁判官溫紹明最終裁定控方不能將被告的招認口供呈堂。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。何見狀遂上前截查被告，並搜出涉案物品。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被告：女警恐嚇坐10年<br />\n<br />\n何續指，。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n辯方盤問時稱，。。。。。。。被告當場否認，女警再指：「堅持話冇就坐10年啦。」最終被告在何不斷催促下，沒看清口供內容便簽署。<br />\n<br />\n溫官最終裁定不能排除被告所言或屬實，控方未能在毫無合理疑點下證明被告必然是自願招供，裁定控方不能將被告的招認口供呈堂。案件表證成立，聆訊今續。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號 ：STCC4438/19"},{"pid":"a8b329ad08d6a112bacf337218687d25805d3ab9","tid":2203416,"uid":61763,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T10:34:08.000Z","msg":"一百單都唔知有冇一單可以咁樣推翻口供"}]}